summary: Found on the boardwalk infront of Riverwood Trader
descriptionHtml:
Some jerk bit my arm off. So, what did I do? slapped on this suit and slapped him til he dropped my arm!

it was an UDDER Discrace! Funny though, as chickens don\'t have udders.

Either rate, here is a chicken outfit for you guys.

It can be found on the eternal boardwalk infront of the ever so whimsical Riverwood Trader
Seriously though, hes a ponce.

Have fun with the full outfit!
author: KirbyPoP or TheRunningDafini
